Insights
Requested permissions:
Camera
allows for scanning QR codes and collecting ambience entropy for XRandom.
Microphone
allows collecting ambience entropy for XRandom.
External storage
to be able to keep wallet backups and restore from backups. No other file types are accessed.
Full network access
enables the app to connect to the Bitcoin network and fetch auxillary data like exchange rates.
Bitcoin is decentralized. There is no server that would hold any of your private data.
